{"tid":1794762,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"兔仔穿過障礙搶嘢食 !!!","createTime":"2019-12-23T11:01:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T15:43:42.000Z","uid":197098,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"650eae6cc63851ed0ec2a06177d6a95a19de7549","tid":1794762,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T11:01:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/S4SUpwhJVjo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FS4SUpwhJVjo&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwRYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=6240a4d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/S4SUpwhJVjo</a>"},{"pid":"5b531dfd563492c102c9a7714a4861392291da12","tid":1794762,"uid":250511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T11:02:58.000Z","msg":"死兔.jpg"},{"pid":"494b4f2c12af4e241eec46074a09775b8a516c59","tid":1794762,"uid":124400,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T11:27:25.000Z","msg":"呢D片根本同抖音d寵物片一樣, 為搏眼球而拍"},{"pid":"22ce05ede401688706ff5d893d16ebc09c354df1","tid":1794762,"uid":233843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T12:02:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d38a815e83963417355f1713fdb9924dd509a9d2","tid":1794762,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T13:28:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">兔子<span style=\"color: red;\">側面看某東西就代表正面看某東西</span>。牠們正前方和下方是盲點，除了這兩個盲點外，牠們幾乎可以看到360度。(所以有時食物在牠下巴下面睇唔到)&nbsp;<span style=\"color: red;\">你在牠後面也會看到你</span>。兔子只有向著前方大約30度範圍，才可以有立體影像。牠們的脊椎就像軟骨那麼脆弱, 另外也有遠視。所以牠們不是無視你，你是在他們視線範圍之內。</span>"},{"pid":"2b551b09efa8de4aeffb87705c0d12097dbbc986","tid":1794762,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T15:39:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兔子是應該要被絕育</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">根據美國兔子協會(House Rabbit Society):</span><br />\n<br />\n1. 兔子是被捕獵動物(Prey animal), 是大自然內每個捕獵者(Predator)的目標, 狗吠聲、消防車叫聲、小孩尖叫、雷暴等也會嚇驚兔子, 所以不建議帶出外散步。兔子是全世界其中一個最多被棄養的動物(在美國排第3最多被棄養), 很多人將牠放生, 這樣會令兔子十分恐慌, 而且沒有覓食能力(寵物兔和野兔是不同), 有些人送給兔協, 但容納不到那麼龐大的數目。<br />\n<br />\n2. 絕育後會大大減少因荷爾蒙控制而霸地盤，不會隨地去廁所 (兔子是不需要訓練去廁所，只要廁所內有紙棉和乾草和夠大便可以, 建議用貓廁所)<br />\n<br />\n3. 荷爾蒙減少令攻擊性減少，更加溫馴和親人，也會活得更開心。如果想將2隻兔合養(做夫妻/好朋友)要先絕育才容易建立關係, 否則有機會打架！<br />\n<br />\n4. 兔子是很容易患上生殖器病動物，所以絕育會令到更健康和長壽！<br />\n<br />\n5. 減少過量繁殖(和棄養後所面對的困境)，繁殖得快和多。"},{"pid":"0b17f7f32e79f2551d15cac471a8662b9e7b9779","tid":1794762,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T08:19:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b8b99c158e688db85104c3016b849459c8f2aa","tid":1794762,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T15:21:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>Merry Christmas! May the beauty of the holidays warm your spirit!</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1f617ca62e104f6a526ab909686dfddaacb033c","tid":1794762,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T15:43:42.000Z","msg":"五毛POST"}]}